<title>Lalpa Nasem Hitiu !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. I damsungun Sem meng hi tiu ,
 Gitloh buoina kal ahin;
 Danleh Lalpa Isu zalin.
 Lallukhuk lopi chang tai tiu.

[V2]
 Aw lei Lallukkhuk te hin,
 Kumsawt gam tun thei puon au;
 Pielgala hinna Lallukhuk chu.
 Aw, thokit chate chun khu tau au.

[V3]
 2. Ma khan Eden huon thiengtho ah,
 Evi leh Adamte kha;
 Suihlung mawla nga bang lengsa'
 Gitlohnan a hihdanglam tai.

[V4]
 3. Sepgimna leh puokgikna cheng,
 Chu lui galah bei tana;
 A kumsawt gam nuomtak achun,
 Hukhinte laituol leng unau.

[V5]
 4. Ka ngak zing ui Immanuel,
 Lungkhamna gamthip ahin;
 Dan leh Kanaan gam hawih achun,
 Lungdeihte tawh lengkhawm tang kau.</lyrics>
</song>